headline: Better Dividend Stock: Federal Realty vs. AGNC Investment
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) and AGNC Investment (NASDAQ: AGNC) are both structured as real estate investment trusts (REITs).  What does Federal Realty do?  Federal Realty is actually a pretty simple company to understand.
